title: [Western Waterway, Saewehna]
description: Silver glints on the dark ocean's surface, the moon's rays sparkling along the ripples as far as the eye can see.  Black forms float on the water in the distance, indiscernible at this distance.  A chilled ocean breeze blows, roughing up the ocean stillness.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, southeast, south, west
